description: Qt is cross-platform application and UI framework which allows you to develop applications and user interfaces once, and deploy them across Windows, Mac, Linux/X11, embedded Linux, Windows CE, Symbian, Maemo, MeeGo, iOS and Android without rewriting the source code.
